000C39  1               ; ; SECTOR_MAP ($BC39): translate the requested logical sector into a physical
000C39  1               ; ; track/sector, deciding whether a seek/reseek is needed and whether the host
000C39  1               ; ; buffer move runs forward (read) or is staged (write).
000C39  1               ; ; ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
