000C39  1               ;         JR NZ,SM_RET                     ; $BD45  20 DB      not a hard error -> SM_RET ($BD22)
000C39  1               ;         JP BIOS_ERR                      ; $BD47  C3 C6 FE   hard error -> BIOS error handler
000C39  1               ;         NOP                              ; $BD4A  00         pad to the page-table boundary
