0010EF  1               ; HANDOFF  ($10EF) -- copy runtime, relocate RWTS to $BA00, switch to the Z-80
0010EF  1               ; ============================================================================
0010EF  1               ; [AI] SoftCard found. Copy $13EF-$13FF -> $03EF (the page-3 control tail), then
0010EF  1               ;      self-modify this routine first 3 bytes at $1000 into JMP $FA00 (the Z-80 BIOS
0010EF  1               ;      warm-entry), so a later re-entry lands in CP/M. PAGE_COPY then relocates the
0010EF  1               ;      RWTS: $0A00 -> $BA00 (6 pages) and copies the rest of the RWTS image + the Z-80
0010EF  1               ;      disk glue into LC RAM (the $0A97 6-page and $0AA3 $17-page blocks), patching the
0010EF  1               ;      run-time constant at $BC08. JSR $BBEB re-inits the IOB.
0010EF  1               HANDOFF:
0010EF  1  A0 10                LDY #$10                     ; $10EF  A0 10
0010F1  1               HANDOFF_1:
0010F1  1  B9 EF 13             LDA $13EF,Y                  ; $10F1  B9 EF 13
0010F4  1  99 EF 03             STA $03EF,Y                  ; $10F4  99 EF 03
0010F7  1  88                   DEY                          ; $10F7  88
0010F8  1  D0 F7                BNE HANDOFF_1                   ; $10F8  D0 F7
0010FA  1  A9 C3                LDA #$C3                     ; $10FA  A9 C3
0010FC  1  8D 00 10             STA LOAD_CPM                   ; $10FC  8D 00 10
0010FF  1  A9 00                LDA #$00                     ; $10FF  A9 00
