0011C7  1               ;      area) that CP/M reuses. The 441-byte .res below spans this image low half.
0011C7  1  00 00 00 00          .res    441, $00    ; $11C7  fill
0011CB  1  00 00 00 00  
0011CF  1  00 00 00 00  
