001380  1               ;      vectors (low-high), copied with this image to $0380-$0395 (Z-80 $F380). Each BIOS
001380  1               ;      CONST/CONIN/CONOUT/READER/PUNCH/LIST primitive JMPs through one of these cells:
001380  1               ;        $0380 $FB14 Console Status   $0382 $FB33 Console In #1   $0384 $FB33 Console In #2
001380  1               ;        $0386 $FCB5 Console Out #1   $0388 $FCB5 Console Out #2  $038A $FE66 Reader In #1
001380  1               ;        $038C $FE66 Reader In #2     $038E $FE60 Punch Out #1    $0390 $FE60 Punch Out #2
